well as on the board of directors for sonic corp prior to dicks ms hobart spent  years at pepsico in various strategic planning and marketing roles culminating in serving as chief marketing officer of carbonated soft drinks innorth america prior to that she spent five years in banking at wells fargo and jpmorgan chase ms hobart is a graduate of the university of pennsylvania and holds an mba from stanford university basic compensation total annual compensation usd 7 restricted stock awards usd  longterm incentive plans usd  all other usd 67 fiscal year total usd  options compensation   quantity market value exercisable   unexercisable   exercised   basic compensation name fiscal year total edward stack  lauren hobart  william colombo  lee belitsky  holly tyson  keri jones  as of   jan  » view all officers related topics stocksstock screenersmiscellaneous specialty retailers hobart lauren r top holdings whalewisdom search all search f filers only search sec filer search stocks only search mgmt inv cos only etfs only search active hobart lauren r • coraopolis pa how do i update this listing hobart lauren r is based out of coraopolis whalewisdom has at least  insider transactions form  in our database for hobart lauren r summary dg insider form  create email alert × email notification log in or signup to see more advanced email alert options such as selecting any type of sec form multiple filers or classes of filers and much more or to simply have an email sent to you whenever we receive a new f filing from hobart lauren r enter your email address below and choose submit your email cancel contact info hobart lauren r  court street coraopolis pa    7 business phone 7 sec sic coderetailmiscellaneous shopping goods stores recent sec filings  filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on 6  filed on 6  filed on 6  filed on 6  filed on 7  filed on   filed on  schedule d and g events since  subscription required form   nonderivative insider transactions since  loading elevate yo